## 1. Who we are

Flintlock ("we", "us", "our") is a digital studio operated by Flintlock Agency, based in Casablanca, Morocco. We provide web development, AI integration, automation, and cybersecurity services.

**Website:** https://flintlockagency.com
**Email:** contact@flintlockagency.com
**Phone:** +212 706-570686

## 2. What data we collect

### 2.1 Contact form submissions
When you fill out our contact form, we collect:
- Your name
- Your email address
- Your message content

This data is processed by a Cloudflare Worker and delivered to our email inbox via Resend (https://resend.com).

### 2.2 Lead magnet downloads
When you download our ebook, we collect:
- Your email address

This is used solely to deliver the download link and is stored for marketing communications (with your consent).

### 2.3 Analytics
We use **Plausible Analytics** (https://plausible.io), a privacy-friendly, cookieless analytics tool. Plausible does not use cookies, does not collect personal data, and is fully compliant with GDPR, CCPA, and PECR.

### 2.4 Calendly scheduling
When you book a call via Calendly, Calendly collects your name, email, and scheduling preferences. This is governed by [Calendly's own privacy policy](https://calendly.com/privacy).

## 3. How we use your data

We use your data to:
- Respond to your inquiries
- Deliver requested resources (ebook downloads)
- Schedule and conduct discovery calls
- Improve our website (via anonymous analytics)

## 4. Legal basis for processing

Under GDPR, our legal basis for processing is:
- **Consent:** When you submit a form or download a resource
- **Legitimate interest:** When we respond to business inquiries
- **Contract:** When we enter into a service agreement

## 5. Data sharing

We do **not** sell your personal data. We share it only with:
- **Cloudflare Workers + Resend** — form processing and email delivery (data processor)
- **Plausible Analytics** — anonymous website analytics (no personal data)
- **Calendly** — scheduling (data processor)

## 6. Data retention

- Contact form submissions: retained for 2 years
- Lead magnet emails: retained until you unsubscribe
- Analytics data: aggregated, anonymous, retained indefinitely

## 7. Your rights

Under GDPR, you have the right to:
- **Access** your personal data
- **Rectify** inaccurate data
- **Erase** your data ("right to be forgotten")
- **Object** to processing
- **Port** your data
- **Withdraw consent** at any time

To exercise any of these rights, email us at contact@flintlockagency.com.

## 8. Cookies

This website uses **no tracking cookies**. Plausible Analytics is cookieless by design. The only cookies that may be set are functional cookies required for the website to operate.

## 9. International data transfers

Our servers are hosted by Cloudflare. Data may be processed in data centers outside the EU. Cloudflare maintains [GDPR compliance](https://www.cloudflare.com/gdpr/) and provides appropriate safeguards for international transfers.

## 10. Changes to this policy

We may update this policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top indicates the most recent revision.

